name: The Dream Team Legend 1992 USA
description: The 1992 United States men's Olympic basketball team, nicknamed the "Dream Team", was the first American Olympic team to feature active professional players from the National Basketball Association. The team has been described by American and international journalists as the greatest sports team ever assembled. Wikipedia
